title: Two Of The Most Powerful Words, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO34
description: What are two of the most powerful words in the English language? According to Andy Frisella, they are "Thank" and "You." Whether you're pursuing success in business or happiness in life, cultivating gratitude is essential.
